<p>If you have found this page you may have encountered the user-agent string of our crawler application.</p>

<p>The Tübingen University Library (Universitätsbibliothek Tübingen) maintains several search engines for bibliographic metadata, there being:
    <ul>
        <li>1. <a href="https://ixtheo.de" target="_blank">IxTheo</a> (search for theological articles, books etc.)</li>
        <li>2. <a href="https://relbib.de" target="_blank">RelBib</a> (search for articles, books etc. relating to the study of religion)</li>
